Storys.content: I was born and raised in Vietnam. I have been exposed to computers since I was 12 years old and really like it. I am also interested in design. Sometime, I wonder if I should be a designer or a programmer because I like both. So I choose Front End developer to enjoy both.

A little bit about me

In my free time, I like to watch Youtube and playing games. My favorite youtuber are MixiGaming. Some games I usually play are Arena Of Valor and League of Legends. Also, I love collecting models of my favorite characters, such as: Dragon Ball, One Piece,...
